00118 long
00119 GUISUMOViewParent::onCmdMakeSnapshot(FXObject*, FXSelector, void*) {
00120     // get the new file name
00121     FXFileDialog opendialog(this, "Save Snapshot");
00122     opendialog.setIcon(GUIIconSubSys::getIcon(ICON_EMPTY));
00123     opendialog.setSelectMode(SELECTFILE_ANY);
00124     opendialog.setPatternList("All Image Files (*.gif, *.bmp, *.xpm, *.pcx, *.ico, *.rgb, *.xbm, *.tga, *.png, *.jpg, *.jpeg, *.tif, *.tiff, *.ps, *.eps, *.pdf, *.svg, *.tex, *.pgf)\n"
00125                               "GIF Image (*.gif)\nBMP Image (*.bmp)\nXPM Image (*.xpm)\nPCX Image (*.pcx)\nICO Image (*.ico)\n"
00126                               "RGB Image (*.rgb)\nXBM Image (*.xbm)\nTARGA Image (*.tga)\nPNG Image  (*.png)\n"
00127                               "JPEG Image (*.jpg, *.jpeg)\nTIFF Image (*.tif, *.tiff)\n"
00128                               "Postscript (*.ps)\nEncapsulated Postscript (*.eps)\nPortable Document Format (*.pdf)\n"
00129                               "Scalable Vector Graphics (*.svg)\nLATEX text strings (*.tex)\nPortable LaTeX Graphics (*.pgf)\n"
00130                               "All Files (*)");
00131     if (gCurrentFolder.length() != 0) {
00132         opendialog.setDirectory(gCurrentFolder);
00133     }
00134     if (!opendialog.execute() || !MFXUtils::userPermitsOverwritingWhenFileExists(this, opendialog.getFilename())) {
00135         return 1;
00136     }
00137     gCurrentFolder = opendialog.getDirectory();
00138     std::string file = opendialog.getFilename().text();
00139     std::string error = myView->makeSnapshot(file);
00140     if (error != "") {
00141         FXMessageBox::error(this, MBOX_OK, "Saving failed.", error.c_str());
00142     }
00143     return 1;
00144 }

00147 long
00148 GUISUMOViewParent::onCmdLocate(FXObject*, FXSelector sel, void*) {
00149     GUIGlObjectType type;
00150     std::vector<GUIGlID> ids;
00151     GUIIcon icon;
00152     std::string title;
00153     switch (FXSELID(sel)) {
00154         case MID_LOCATEJUNCTION:
00155             type = GLO_JUNCTION;
00156             ids = static_cast<GUINet*>(GUINet::getInstance())->getJunctionIDs(myParent->listInternal());
00157             icon = ICON_LOCATEJUNCTION;
00158             title = "Junction Chooser";
00159             break;
00160         case MID_LOCATEEDGE:
00161             type = GLO_EDGE;
00162             ids = GUIEdge::getIDs(myParent->listInternal());
00163             icon = ICON_LOCATEEDGE;
00164             title = "Edge Chooser";
00165             break;
00166         case MID_LOCATEVEHICLE:
00167             type = GLO_VEHICLE;
00168             static_cast<GUIVehicleControl&>(MSNet::getInstance()->getVehicleControl()).insertVehicleIDs(ids);
00169             icon = ICON_LOCATEVEHICLE;
00170             title = "Vehicle Chooser";
00171             break;
00172         case MID_LOCATETLS:
00173             type = GLO_TLLOGIC;
00174             ids = static_cast<GUINet*>(GUINet::getInstance())->getTLSIDs();
00175             icon = ICON_LOCATETLS;
00176             title = "Traffic Lights Chooser";
00177             break;
00178         case MID_LOCATEADD:
00179             type = GLO_ADDITIONAL;
00180             ids = GUIGlObject_AbstractAdd::getIDList();
00181             icon = ICON_LOCATEADD;
00182             title = "Additional Objects Chooser";
00183             break;
00184         case MID_LOCATESHAPE:
00185             type = GLO_SHAPE;
00186             ids = static_cast<GUIShapeContainer&>(GUINet::getInstance()->getShapeContainer()).getShapeIDs();
00187             icon = ICON_LOCATESHAPE;
00188             title = "Shape Chooser";
00189             break;
00190         default:
00191             throw ProcessError("Unknown Message ID in onCmdLocate");
00192     }
00193     myLocatorPopup->popdown();
00194     myLocatorButton->killFocus();
00195     myLocatorPopup->update();
00196     GUIDialog_GLObjChooser* chooser = new GUIDialog_GLObjChooser(
00197         this, GUIIconSubSys::getIcon(icon), title.c_str(), type, ids, GUIGlObjectStorage::gIDStorage);
00198     chooser->create();
00199     chooser->show();
00200     return 1;
00201 }

00212 bool
00213 GUISUMOViewParent::isSelected(GUIGlObject* o) const {
00214     GUIGlObjectType type = o->getType();
00215     if (gSelected.isSelected(type, o->getGlID())) {
00216         return true;
00217     } else if (type == GLO_EDGE) {
00218         GUIEdge* edge = dynamic_cast<GUIEdge*>(o);
00219         assert(edge);
00220         size_t noLanes = edge->getLanes().size();
00221         for (size_t j = 0; j < noLanes; ++j) {
00222             const GUILaneWrapper& l = edge->getLaneGeometry(j);
00223             if (gSelected.isSelected(GLO_LANE, l.getGlID())) {
00224                 return true;
00225             }
00226         }
00227         return false;
00228     } else {
00229         return false;
00230     }
00231 }
